==English==
===Etymology===
Back-formation from ''[[fluorescence]]''
===Intransitive verb===
# ''(Physics)'' To emit [[electromagnetic radiation]], especially [[visible]] light, when [[absorb]]ing radiation of some other [[wavelength]].
# (Of colours) to be very [[bright]], easy to see, [[dayglo]].
